@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.14 + tmp + 0.91) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.17)))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.67) + wp.sin(v1 + 0.47)) * wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.93)))
    v0 = 0.36
    data[tid] = v0
